						<summary>

						<p>This is also damaged and worn out. It registers the conferment of the right or <hi rend="italic">kāval</hi> (watch) with its remuneration of the <hi rend="italic">maḍichchilai-vari</hi> probably collected from the hawkers of goods at the place, granted by Achchutarāya-Tummuśi-Nāyakkar to the <hi rend="italic">Padineṇ-vishayattār</hi> of Kīḻaikkarai <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Niṉaittadu-muḍittāṉ-paṭṭiṉam.</p>						

